                    <span>Zero To One Million is a very informative book that any future entrepreneur or anyone planning to start a business of their own should read and benefit from. The 100 steps to building a company to $1 million in sales is worth the cost of the book alone. I found the information easy to read and follow and, more importantly, easy to put into practice. Mr. Allis was able to provide me with a step by step guide on how to not only get started with a business, but also how to maintain and grow it. I would highly recommend this book to anyone just starting out with a business of their own or any small business owners looking for an extra "edge" to stimulate growth. The web marketing ideas and information on search engine optimization were of immense value to me in my job. Zero To One Million is definitely a must buy!</span>
                  
